title: Tournament of Chompions: Wendy’s v. Wingstop with Matt Selman
itunes:title: Tournament of Chompions: Wendy’s v. Wingstop with Matt Selman
description:
The second matchup of the Munch Madness 2017 semifinals finds returning guest Matt Selman (The Simpsons) discussing his history as Mitch’s boss, and his role in helping to create fictional chain restaurant Cletus’ Chicken Shack. Can tournament favorite Wendy’s, minus its signature Spicy Chicken Sandwich due to a ban from Commissioner Susser, prevail over surprise first round winner Wingstop? Plus, a closely contested rematch of The Wiger Challenge. Make YOUR chompion predictions @ www.feralaudio.com/chompions2017

Want more Doughboys? Check out our Patreon!: https://patreon.com/doughboys
